'''蘆溝龍屬'''（[[學名|屬名]]：{{lang|la|''Lukousaurus''}}）是分類地位有爭議的[[主龍形下綱|主龍形下綱]]動物，生存於[[侏羅紀|早侏羅世]][[辛涅繆爾期|辛涅繆爾期]]<ref name = Luo1994>{{ cite book | last1 = Luo | first1 = Z.-X. | last2 = Wu | first2 = X.-C. | chapter = The small vertebrate fauna of the lower Lufeng Formation, Yunnan | editor1-last = Fraser | editor1-first = N. C. | editor2-last = Sues | editor2-first = H. D. | title = ''In the Shadow of the Dinosaurs: Early Mesozoic Tetrapods'' | url = https://archive.org/details/shadowdinosaurse00libg | publisher = [[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]] | year = 1994 | isbn = 0-521-45242-2 | page = [https://archive.org/details/shadowdinosaurse00libg/page/n254 251]-270 }}</ref>至[[赫塘期|赫塘期]]<ref name = Mao2020>{{ Cite journal | last1 = Mao | first1 = L. | last2 = Xing | first2 = L. | last3 = Zhang | first3 = J. | last4 = Wang | first4 = T. | last5 = Wang | first5 = D. | year = 2020 | title = Revisiting the world famous Lufeng Formation dinosaur fauna: new approaches to old problems | journal = ''Historical Biology'' | volume = 32 | issue = 8 | pages = 1062-1070 | doi = 10.1080/08912963.2018.1563784 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/330085281_Revisiting_the_world_famous_Lufeng_Formation_dinosaur_fauna_new_approaches_to_old_problems }}</ref>，已知的化石包含不完整的頭骨、牙齒、前肢與後腿骨骼，皆發現於[[中國|中國]][[雲南省|雲南省]]中北部的[[祿豐盆地|祿豐盆地]]<ref name = Young1948>{{ Cite journal | last1 = Young | first1 = C. C. | year = 1948 | title = On Two New Saurischians From Lufeng, Yunnan | journal = ''Bulletin of the Geological Society of China'' | volume = 28 | issue = 1-2 | pages = 75-90 | doi = 10.1111/j.1755-6724.1948.mp281-2007.x | url = }}</ref><ref name = Simmons1965>{{ Cite journal | last1 = Simmons | first1 = D. J. | year = 1965 | title = The non-therapsid reptiles of the Lufeng Basin, Yunnan, China | journal = ''Fieldiana: Geology'' | volume = 15 | pages = 1-93 | doi = 10.5962/bhl.title.5426 | url = https://dinodata.de/dinothek/pdf_t/1965/nontherapsidrept151simm_dd.pdf }}</ref>。蘆溝龍長期被歸類為[[角鼻龍類|角鼻龍類]]<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Olshevsky | first1 = G. | year = 1991 | title = A revision of the parainfraclass Archosauria Cope, 1869, excluding the advanced Crocodylia | journal = ''Mesozoic Meanderings 2'' | location = San Diego | page = 1-196 | url = http://www.miketaylor.org.uk/tmp/Olshevsky_1991_A_revision_of_the_parainfraclass_Archosauria_Cope_1869_excluding_the_advanced_Crocodylia.pdf | access-date = 2020-12-07 | archive-date = 2018-08-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180819050626/http://www.miketaylor.org.uk/tmp/Olshevsky_1991_A_revision_of_the_parainfraclass_Archosauria_Cope_1869_excluding_the_advanced_Crocodylia.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>或[[虛骨龍類|虛骨龍類]]恐龍<ref name = Young1940>{{ Cite journal | last1 = Young | first1 = C. C. | year = 1940 | title = Preliminary Notes on the Lufeng Vertebrate Fossils | journal = ''Bulletin of the Geological Society of China'' | volume = 20 | issue = 3-4 | pages = 235-239 | doi = 10.1111/j.1755-6724.1940.mp203-4003.x | url = }}</ref>，並作為這兩個類群在[[東亞|東亞]]首批被發表的成員之一<ref name = Simmons1965/>，同時也是[[亞洲|亞洲]]已知最早的[[獸腳類|獸腳類]]恐龍<ref name = Molina-Pérez>{{ cite book | author = Molina-Pérez, R.; Larramendi, A. | others = (譯) Connolly, D.; Cruz, G. A. R. | title = 
''Dinosaur Facts and Figures: The Theropods and Other Dinosauriformes'' | publisher = [[Princeton_University_Press|Princeton University Press]] | year = 2019 | isbn = 978-0-691-18031-1 | page = 27, 112, 255 }}</ref>。但2000年代起，開始有[[古生物學家|古生物學家]]注意到蘆溝龍的頭骨缺少獸腳類的若干重要特徵，因而認為蘆溝龍可能不屬於獸腳類，反而更接近非恐龍的[[偽鱷類|偽鱷類]]<ref name = Irmis2004>{{Cite journal | last1 = Irmis | first1 = R. B. | year = 2004 | title = First report of ''Megapnosaurus'' (Theropoda: Coelophysoidea) from China | journal = ''PaleoBios'' | volume = 24 | issue = 3 | pages = 11-18 | issn = 0031-0298 | doi =  | url = https://ucmp.berkeley.edu/research/paleobios/paleobios-back-issues/2004-2000/ | access-date = 2020-12-07 | archive-date = 2020-11-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201130020438/https://ucmp.berkeley.edu/research/paleobios/paleobios-back-issues/2004-2000/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name = Knoll2012>{{Cite journal | last1 = Knoll | first1 = F. | last2 = Rohrberg | first2 = K. | year = 2012 | title = CT scanning, rapid prototyping and re-examination of a partial skull of a basal crocodylomorph from the Late Triassic of Germany | journal = ''Swiss Journal of Geosciences'' | volume = 105 | pages = 109-115 | issn = 1661-8726 | doi = 10.1007/s00015-012-0094-4 | url = https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00015-012-0094-4 | access-date = 2020-12-07 | archive-date = 2018-06-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180617185909/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs00015-012-0094-4 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 發現歷史 ==
[[File:Xingxiulong-1.jpg|left]]
蘆溝龍的化石最早於1930年代發現於[[中國|中國]][[雲南省_(中華民國)|雲南省]][[祿豐縣|祿豐縣]]中部的黃家田（今名張家窪{{noteTag|1=楊鍾健曾指黃家田至1974年已更名為「張家凹」<ref name = Young1974>{{Cite journal | author = 杨钟健 | year = 1974 | title = 云南禄丰兽孔类新材料 | journal = 古脊椎动物与古人类 | volume = 12 | issue = 2 | pages = 111-114 | doi =  | url = http://www.ivpp.cas.cn/cbw/gjzdwxb/xbwzxz/200905/W020090813377588444260.pdf | access-date = 2020-12-08 | archive-date = 2020-05-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200517143225/http://www.ivpp.cas.cn/cbw/gjzdwxb/xbwzxz/200905/W020090813377588444260.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，然今所稱祿豐縣之張家凹位於該縣南部。卞美年於1940年提及黃家田位於「二鑽山以南約二[[里|里]]地」<ref name = Bien1940>{{Cite journal | last1 = Bien | first1 = M. N. | year = 1940 | title = Discovery of Triassic Saurischian and Primitive Mammalian Remains at Lufeng, Yunnan | journal = ''Bulletin of the Geological Society of China'' | volume = 20 | issue = 3-4 | pages = 225-234 | doi = 10.1111/j.1755-6724.1940.mp203-4002.x | url = http://www.lfbwg.cn/file_read.aspx?id=88 | access-date = 2020-12-08 | archive-date = 2021-02-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210228103019/http://lfbwg.cn/file_read.aspx?ID=88 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，據孫艾玲等人在1985年報告中的附圖研判，黃家田的位置應與張家窪重合<ref name = Sun1985>{{ Cite journal | author = 孙艾玲, 崔贵海, 李雨和, 吴肖春 | year = 1985 | title = 禄丰蜥龙动物群的组成及初步分析 | journal = 古脊椎动物学报 | volume = 23 | issue = 1 | pages = 1-12 | issn = 1000-9418 | doi = | url = http://www.ivpp.ac.cn/cbw/gjzdwxb/xbwzxz/200903/P020100316284818819490.pdf }}</ref>。}}），以及黃家田北北西方向約1公里的大衝，由侏羅紀時期的{{le|祿豐組|Lufeng Formation}}[[張家坳段|張家坳段]]地層出土<ref name = Mao2020/>，包含頭骨前部、牙齒與右[[肱骨|肱骨]]的近端<ref name = Simmons1965/>，後於1940年由中國古生物學家[[楊鍾健|楊鍾健]]在一份祿豐古脊椎動物的初步研究報告中將其命名為蘆溝龍。當時隨蘆溝龍一同在祿豐出土的化石尚未整理完畢，因此楊鍾健只有粗略的介紹蘆溝龍的化石<ref name = Young1940/>，直至1948年，楊鍾健才首次發表蘆溝龍的詳細敘述<ref name = Young1948/>。因為這個緣故，一些文章或刊物會將蘆溝龍的命名資訊標註為「Young, 1948」<ref name = Luo1994/><ref name = Molina-Pérez/><ref name = Sun1985/>，而非「Young, 1940」。

在後續的挖掘工作中，蘆溝龍的右肱骨遠端、部分[[脛骨|脛骨]]與[[腓骨|腓骨]]也在黃家田以西約1公里的沙灣村被發現，屬於年代稍老的祿豐組[[沙灣段|沙灣段]]。此外，蘆溝龍的頭骨在附近的另一個村落黑果棚也有紀錄<ref name = Simmons1965/>。

蘆溝龍的屬名意為「盧溝蜥蜴」，其「盧溝」並非直指發現地，而是指當時[[北平|北平]]城外的[[盧溝橋|盧溝橋]]{{noteTag|1=「盧溝」亦有作「蘆溝」者，但中文約定俗成將''Lukousaurus''譯為蘆溝龍<ref name = Sun1985/>。}}。是時中國正值[[中國抗日戰爭|抗日戰爭]]，許多化石挖掘工作都是在艱困的環境下進行，楊鍾健取戰爭爆發地盧溝橋之名，意在使蘆溝龍成為抗戰艱難時期的象徵。[[模式種|模式種]]是'''尹氏蘆溝龍'''（''L. yini''），種名係表揚當時帶領研究工作，曾任[[中央地質調查所|中央地質調查所]]副所長的古生物學家[[尹贊勛|尹贊勛]]<ref name = Young1948/>。

== 形態描述 ==
=== 頭骨 ===
由於盧溝龍的化石都很破碎，因此學界對其所知很有限。現有兩具已被正式描述的不完整頭骨（都只包含前段）{{noteTag|1=古生物學家{{le|大衛·諾曼|David B. Norman}}在《The Dinosauria》一書中提及，另一位古生物學家{{le|雷夫·莫納|Ralph Molnar}}向他提到在祿豐還發現了另外兩具盧溝龍頭骨，但也都只剩前段<ref name = Norman/>。}}都相當小，[[顱骨|顱骨]]較完整的正模標本（[[中國科學院古脊椎動物與古人類研究所|中國科學院古脊椎動物與古人類研究所]]編號V23）保存長度（吻端至眼眶中段）只有大約7公分，顯示盧溝龍的體型不大；但與其他小型獸腳類恐龍相比，盧溝龍的吻部較為寬厚。正模標本的鼻孔很小，直徑只有0.5公分；同時其三角形的[[眶前孔|眶前孔]]相對寬大，右側眶前孔寬0.2公分。眼眶外緣前半段相當圓潤。牙列短，牙齒扁平且向後彎曲，後側稜脊帶有細小的鋸齒，此與一般的獸腳類恐龍相同<ref name = Young1948/><ref name = Norman>{{ cite book | last1 = Norman | first1 = D. B. | chapter = Problematic Theropoda: "Coelurosaurus" | editor1-last = Weishampel | editor1-first = D. B. | editor2-last = Dodson | editor2-first = P. | editor3-last = Osmólska | editor3-first = H. | title = 
''The Dinosauria'' | publisher = [[University_of_California_Press|University of California Press]] | year = 1990 | isbn = 0-520-06726-6 | page = 280-305 }}</ref>。

發現於黑果棚的頭骨（[[輔仁大學北平時期|北平輔仁大學]]編號CUP 2092，今去向不詳）顯示，蘆溝龍的下頜具有小而位高的[[下頜孔|下頜孔]]（mandibular fenestra），[[前關節骨|前關節骨]]（prearticular）前端貌似指向前方。此外在這具保存狀況不佳的頭骨中，[[隅骨|隅骨]]較大以至蓋過其上方的[[上隅骨|上隅骨]]，甚至到達下頜骨的上緣<ref name = Simmons1965/>。

=== 體型 ===
古生物學家魯本·莫里納-裴雷茲（Rubén Molina-Pérez）與阿西爾·拉羅曼迪（Asier Larramendi）以盧溝龍的最大個體化石——編號V271的肱骨估算，若蘆溝龍屬於角鼻龍類，其全長將有4公尺，臀高1.2公尺，體重約120公斤<ref name = Molina-Pérez/>。

